com.vmware.snapservice.clusters.virtual_machines

  • Packages that use com.vmware.snapservice.clusters.virtual_machines 
    Package Description
    com.vmware.snapservice.clusters
    The com.vmware.snapservice.clusters package provides interfaces for managing protection groups and snapshots in a vSAN cluster.
    com.vmware.snapservice.clusters.virtual_machines
    The com.vmware.snapservice.clusters.virtual_machines package provides interfaces for managing virtual machines in a vSAN cluster.

    VirtualMachinesFactory
